---
title: Rosemary Mushroom Burger & Fries with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Parmesan Crisps
description: Use nature’s patties – large portabello mushroom cups – in place of meat to make these scrumptious veggie burgers. Give them a little brush with rosemary-infused oil and top them with oven-baked Parmesan crisps to create a dinner that's so much better than the local burger joint.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-field-mushroom-burger-fbd7bd4a.jpg
